title: Wildfire Worlds Alpha v0.034 (Discontinued Project)
description:
Wildfire Worlds was an awesome Indie project that started back around 2012. The only objective of the game is to raise hell with your little minions. Unfortunately, the creators of the game decided to stop working on the game in late 2013/early 2014. Because of this, I've decided to upload the latest and last version of the game to TPB to keep the flame going.

Just run the installer to install.

You can check out the game's old website here: http://wildfireworlds.com/

Enjoy!
